<i>noun</i>: 간결성 [간결썽] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>간결성 [간결썽]</dt><br>
<dd>brevity; conciseness</dd><br>
<dd>글이나 말, 혹은 예술 작품 등이 군더더기가 없고 간단하며 깔끔한 성질.</dd><br>
<dd>The quality of being simple and easy without anything superfluous in a certain writing, speech or art.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>